<section class="article-table-of-contents" data-component="articleToc">
			<ol class="article-table-of-contents__list">
			<ul>
<li><a href="#sec2">Empirical Motivation: Structure In Application’s Traffic</a></li>
<li><a href="#sec3">Traditional Datacenter Network Topology Design</a></li>
<li><a href="#sec4">Paradigm Shift: Reconfigurable Topologies and its Enabling Optical Technologies</a></li>
<li><a href="#sec5">The Spectrum of Topology Engineering Solutions</a></li>
<li><a href="#sec6">Examples of Reconfigurable Datacenter Networks Designs</a></li>
<li><a href="#sec7">Models of Reconfigurable Datacenter Networks</a></li>
