<div id="B24" class="citation"><span class="label">24.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="book"><span class="person-group" data-jats-person-group-type="author"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Mellette</span>, <span class="given-names">W.M. </span></span><span class="etal">et al.</span> </span><span class="chapter-title">RotorNet: A scalable, low-complexity, optical datacenter network</span>. In <span class="source"><em>Proceedings of the ACM SIGCOMM 2017 Conf. on Data Communication.</em></span> <span class="publisher-name">ACM</span> (<span class="year">2017</span>), <span class="fpage">267</span>–<span class="lpage">280</span>.</span></div>
